com.msopentech.odatajclient.engine.communication.request

Interface ODataRequest

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ODataBasicRequest<V,T>, ODataBatchableRequest, ODataStreamedRequest<V,T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ODataBasicRequestImpl, ODataBatchRequest, ODataDeleteRequest, ODataEntityCreateRequest, ODataEntityRequest, ODataEntitySetIteratorRequest, ODataEntitySetRequest, ODataEntityUpdateRequest, ODataGenericRetrieveRequest, ODataInvokeRequest, ODataLinkCollectionRequest, ODataLinkCreateRequest, ODataLinkUpdateRequest, ODataMediaEntityCreateRequest, ODataMediaEntityUpdateRequest, ODataMediaRequest, ODataMetadataRequest, ODataPropertyRequest, ODataPropertyUpdateRequest, ODataRawRequest, ODataRequestImpl, ODataServiceDocumentRequest, ODataStreamedEntityRequestImpl, ODataStreamedRequestImpl, ODataStreamUpdateRequest, ODataValueRequest, ODataValueUpdateRequest

    public interface ODataRequest
    Abstract representation of an OData request. Get instance by using factories.
    See Also:
    ODataCUDRequestFactory, ODataRetrieveRequestFactory, ODataBatchRequestFactory, ODataInvokeRequestFactory, ODataStreamedRequestFactory
